{"tid":39773,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急呼籲] 請各位巴絲注意言辭, 不要再次傷害橘子絲打","createTime":"2016-12-14T18:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T20:04:02.000Z","uid":37264,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe24a6b9fba21ad66bda61633fe2bf878227e68c","tid":39773,"uid":37264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T18:33:48.000Z","msg":"有幾樣野各位巴絲可以做既<br />\n<br />\n1. 如果你身邊有人叫林昆樂, 同時有女性朋友呢一兩日有古怪行為, 請盡快與絲打接觸, 安定其情緒。<br />\n<br />\n2. 有做酒店業既巴絲, 請關注星期三晚自己既logbook有否絲打講既情況發生。<br />\n<br />\n3. 其他唔關事既巴絲, 鳩野唔好講咁多, 唔出聲冇人當你啞。可以既話比多啲支持既說話比絲打, 而唔係落井下石。<br />\n<br />\n4. 切勿起底, 多謝合作。不但影響案情, 呢個moment起底絲打都會好唔開心。<br />\n<br />\n連登今次要團結一致共抗外侮, 支持絲打!"},{"pid":"d99bd90f33c1e6662b262a76659e3484325c7b5e","tid":39773,"uid":37264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T18:36:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95a81bef258e8e781aff35d32c667939f5d53e76","tid":39773,"uid":37264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T18:39:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44a3dad444c9a33ad57182d161fc968c4e3caf81","tid":39773,"uid":37264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T18:39:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a69adb49f851dbc3a74b76e570104fd719529f7","tid":39773,"uid":37264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T18:42:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"198051ebce1090bc791643412e1138d1f403ac4b","tid":39773,"uid":11345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T18:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" 